frames.caption: A woman in a white dress stands on a boat's deck, gazing out at the expansive ocean. The sky is painted with soft hues of blue and gray as the sun sets on the horizon.
frames.description: The scene is set on a boat during sunset, with a woman standing at the railing, looking out at the ocean. The atmosphere is calm and contemplative, with the gentle movement of the water and the soft colors of the sky creating a serene backdrop.

frames.caption: A perfume bottle with a golden cap sits elegantly on a wooden railing, overlooking a vast expanse of calm ocean water. The setting sun casts a warm glow, highlighting the sparkling details within the bottle.
frames.description: The scene captures a serene moment on a boat or waterfront setting, with a focus on a luxurious perfume bottle against the backdrop of the ocean. The atmosphere is tranquil and reflective, enhanced by the gentle lighting of the sunset.
